This is a decent looking movie. Not a dvdrip by any means but still ok.

Audio is also pretty good and IN SYNC despite what people are saying.

For any out of sync problems use GOM Player.  Its free from Google. 
When the movie starts right click and a list of stuff comes up that you can change.  
For sync problems choose AUDIO 
Then SHIFT & < for Backwards, or SHIFT & > Forwards. Then the mouths will sync with the words.
It has never failed to put a movie right for me.
I hope that helps :)
